<item>
            <title>[HIVE-4327] NPE in constant folding with decimal</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HIVE-4327</link>
                <project id="12310843" key="HIVE">Hive</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The query:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;SELECT dec * cast(&apos;123456789012345678901234567890.1234567&apos; as decimal) FROM DECIMAL_PRECISION LIMIT 1&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;fails with an NPE while constant folding. This only happens when the decimal is out of range of max precision.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
